author: Patrick Cc:
description:
Got injured in an accident? You could be click away from a claim worth millions. You can start your claim now with Morgan & Morgan at https://www.forthepeople.com/Patrick without leaving your couch. Remember, it's free unless you win.

Kurt Angle was an Olympic hero and pro wrestling icon—but behind the glory was a man battling unimaginable pain. At one point, he was taking 65 pills a day just to function, spiraling through addiction, arrests, and near-death moments. This is the brutal and tragic story of how one of the toughest athletes in the world nearly lost everything trying to survive a sport the world calls "fake."
